# IJT Test Client — Cursor Rules

Read [`docs/SKILLS.md`](docs/SKILLS.md) for full project context before doing any work.

It covers: project structure, test suite layout, OPC UA conformance patterns, server requirements, fixture design, and common mistakes.

## Critical hygiene rules (always apply)

- **Environments**: `.venv_test` = tests (run_all_tests.py). No separate runtime `.venv` for this client.
- **Pre-commit**: hooks auto-fix formatting/CRLF. If commit is rejected, run `git add -u && git commit` once more.
- **Generated files**: `Types/` in IJT_CSharp_Client is auto-generated — never edit, never format.
- See [`docs/SKILLS.md`](../../../docs/SKILLS.md) for full developer setup and hygiene details.
